Name: GloGo
About the game: In GloGo, you become the ball. Navigate through all the obstacles in your way as you try and complete every level in the shortest time possible. Avoid the dreaded 'Participation Award' and earn your place on the podium with at least a Bronze, Silver, Gold, or Platinum Award! Challenge your friends and see who among you can earn the top award in the shortest time possible!
